subject: Hello,
body:
Hello,
Hope you had a good day.
Please If you have time, write to me so i can sent you a detailed message.

subject: Re:   Hello,
body:
Hello there,

I hope you're doing well. I'm glad to hear from you and I'd be happy to receive more information. Could you please tell me a bit more about what this is regarding? 

Looking forward to your response. Thank you!

Best wishes,
Maureen
